sentences: Jerry Hahn (born September 21, 1940, Alma, Nebraska) is an American jazz guitarist.
Hahn studied at Wichita State University, then moved to San Francisco in 1962, where he played with John Handy (1964–66).

He toured with the 5th Dimension in 1968 and worked with Gary Burton from 1968–69.
